{[showcards W:CA N:C4]

You are East. The bidding has been as shown. Partner led the \CA, dummy played the \C4 

Play the \C8 to encourage a continuation. West will play the \CQ on which you will play the \C2.

West now knows you started with a doubleton, and more importantly, he also knows you want him to play a third \C.

When he next plays the \CK dummy will ruff, but whatever card he ruffs with you will have established a trump trick. When you later win your \SK that will be down 1.}
[Play "W"]CA

